{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbb350c17-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1582"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1582"},"text":"§ 1582.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Temporary housing exempted from provisions of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1553"},"text":"section 1553 of this title","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The requirements of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1553"},"text":"section 1553 of this title","children":[],"tail":" shall not apply to any temporary housing—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbb350c18-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1582/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" for which such requirements have been waived pursuant to section 1575 ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn003178"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn003178"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":" or "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1581"},"text":"section 1581 of this title","children":[],"tail":";"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbb350c19-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1582/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" transferred by the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development to the jurisdiction of the Department of the Army, the Navy, or the Air Force pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1524"},"text":"section 1524 of this title","children":[],"tail":";"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbb350c1a-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1582/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" disposed of by the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development under subchapter II or IV of this chapter for long-term housing or nonhousing use without any requirement for removal where the governing body of the municipality or county has adopted a resolution determining that, on the basis of local need and acceptability, the structures involved are (1) satisfactory for such long-term use or (2) satisfactory for such long-term use if conditions prescribed in such resolution, affecting the physical characteristics of the project, are met: ","children":[{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"Provided","children":[],"tail":", That any such conditions shall not affect the disposal of any temporary housing hereunder, and the United States shall assume no responsibility for compliance with such conditions: "},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"And provided further","children":[],"tail":", That any housing disposed of for housing use in accordance with this subsection shall thereafter be deemed to be housing accommodations, the construction of which was completed after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1947-06-30"},"text":"June 30, 1947","children":[],"tail":", within the meaning of section 4 of the Housing and Rent Act of 1947, as amended, relating to preference or priority to veterans or their families; or"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbb350c1b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s1582/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" disposed of or relinquished by the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development prior to ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1950-04-20"},"text":"April 20, 1950","children":[],"tail":", subject to such requirements or contractual obligations pursuant thereto, where the governing body of the municipality or county on or before "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1950-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 1950","children":[],"tail":", adopts a resolution as provided in (c) "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn003179"},"text":"2","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn003179"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"2","children":[],"tail":" So in original. Probably should be preceded by “subsection”."}],"tail":" above; and any contract obligations to the Federal Government for the removal of such housing shall be relinquished upon the filing of such a resolution with the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbb350c1c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1940-10-14/ch862"},"text":"Oct. 14, 1940, ch. 862","children":[],"tail":", title VI, § 602, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1948-06-28/ch688/s7"},"text":"June 28, 1948, ch. 688, § 7","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1950-04-20/ch94"},"text":"Apr. 20, 1950, ch. 94","children":[],"tail":", title II, § 201, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/64/59"},"text":"64 Stat. 59","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1951-10-26/ch577/s2"},"text":"Oct. 26, 1951, ch. 577, § 2","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/65/648"},"text":"65 Stat. 648","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/174/s5/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–174, § 5(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1965-09-09"},"text":"Sept. 9, 1965","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/79/669"},"text":"79 Stat. 669","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbb350c1d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbb350c1e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idbb350c1f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1575"},"text":"Section 1575 of this title","children":[],"tail":", referred to in subsec. (a), has been omitted from the Code."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section 4 of the Housing and Rent Act of 1947, referred to in subsec. (c), is section 4 of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1947-06-30/ch163/tI"},"text":"act June 30, 1947, ch. 163, title I","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/61/195"},"text":"61 Stat. 195","children":[],"tail":", which was formerly classified to section 1884 of the former Appendix to Title 50, War and National Defense, and has been omitted from the Code."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idbb350c20-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1951—Subsec. (c). Act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1951-10-26"},"text":"Oct. 26, 1951","children":[],"tail":", struck “of World War II” thus making section applicable to veterans of Korean war."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idbb350c21-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"transferOfFunctions","id":"idbb350c22-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Transfer of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For transfer of functions to Secretary of Housing and Urban Development, see note set out under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s1581"},"text":"section 1581 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
